<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/public/img/logo2.jpg" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />

    <title>Conex Speaker Registeration</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/registerStyle.css" />
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container px-4 py-5 mx-auto">
      <div class="card card0">
        <div class="d-flex flex-lg-row flex-column-reverse">
          <div class="card card1">
            <div class="row justify-content-center my-auto">
              <div class="col-md-8 col-10 my-5">
                <div class="row justify-content-center px-3 mb-3"></div>
                <h3
                  class="mb-5 text-center heading"
                  style="font-family: Aclonica"
                >
                  BE A CONEX SPEAKER
                </h3>
                <h6 class="msg-info">Kindly Fill Out the Form</h6>
                <% if (error) { %>
                <h6 style="color: white; background-color: red; padding: 10px">
                  <%= error %>
                </h6>
                <% } %> <% if (message) { %>
                <h6
                  style="color: white; background-color: green; padding: 10px"
                >
                  <%= message %>
                </h6>
                <% } %>
                <form method="POST">
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-control-label text-muted">Name</label>
                    <input
                      type="text"
                      id="name"
                      name="name"
                      placeholder=""
                      class="form-control"
                      required
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-control-label text-muted"
                      >Phone Number</label
                    >
                    <input
                      type="text"
                      id="phoneNumber"
                      name="phoneNumber"
                      placeholder=""
                      class="form-control"
                      required
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-control-label text-muted">Email</label>
                    <input
                      type="email"
                      id="email"
                      name="email"
                      placeholder=""
                      class="form-control"
                      required
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-control-label text-muted"
                      >Location</label
                    >
                    <input
                      type="text"
                      id="location"
                      name="location"
                      placeholder=""
                      class="form-control"
                      required
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-control-label text-muted"
                      >Area of Expertise</label
                    >
                    <input
                      type="text"
                      id="expertise"
                      name="areaOfExpertise"
                      placeholder=""
                      class="form-control"
                      required
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-control-label text-muted"
                      >How Do You Charge?</label
                    >
                    <input
                      type="text"
                      id="charge"
                      name="charge"
                      placeholder="Eg: 2000 Rs/Hour"
                      class="form-control"
                      required
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="row justify-content-center my-3 px-3">
                    <button class="btn-block btn-color" type="submit">
                      Register
                    </button>
                  </div>
                </form>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card card2">
            <div class="my-auto mx-md-5 px-md-5 right">
              <h3 class="text-white">We are more than just a company</h3>
              <small style="font-size: 15px" class="text-white"
                >Conex365 is the high quality E-learning platform that’s
                determined to decrease employability equip people with skills
                and help them become career ready. WE cannot do this alone! We
                need talented influencers and entrepreneurs to join our Conex
                family! It’s time to cascade your wisdom to those who need them
                the most! Become a Conex Speaker for both Conex Plus and Conex
                Edu Plus and help us transform the traditional learning with a
                more dynamic, smart and understandable learning that can be
                suitable for any age group. What’s in it for you? A lot of
                opportunities to fulfill your goals, speed up your career
                progression, market yourself and change lives.<br /><b>
                  Fill in the form and we promise to be in touch within
                  12hrs!</b
                ></small
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
  <script
    src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN"
    crossorigin="anonymous"
  ></script>
  <script
    src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.12.9/umd/popper.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q"
    crossorigin="anonymous"
  ></script>
  <script
    src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl"
    crossorigin="anonymous"
  ></script>
</html>
